{
"#name"
:
{
"install"
:
null
,
"en"
:
"Cross-platform installer for software, skills, and more"
,
"cn"
:
"跨平台安装器，支持软件、skill 等安装"
}
,
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Cross-platform installer — query and install software and skills, with interactive selection, CI/CD auto best-match, or structured output for AI agents"
,
"cn"
:
"跨平台安装器，查询并安装软件和 skill —— 支持交互式选择、CI/CD 自动最佳匹配、AI Agent 结构化输出"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x install [policy] [software]"
:
null
}
,
{
"x install --best <software>"
:
null
}
,
{
"x install --withtool <tool> <software>"
:
null
}
,
{
"x install --search <keyword>"
:
null
}
,
{
"x install --printinfo <software>"
:
null
}
,
{
"x install --printcmd <software>"
:
null
}
,
{
"x install --env"
:
null
}
]
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"不知道该用什么方式装软件？直接 x install 加软件名，\n会列出当前系统所有可用的安装方式，选一个就行。\n也支持批量安装和 skill 安装（skill/* 或 clawhub/* 格式）。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Don't know which method to install software? Just run `x install <software>` to see all available methods for your system and pick one.\nAlso supports batch install and skill installation (skill/* or clawhub/* format).\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"写脚本自动装软件？三种方式按需选择：\n--best 按优先级自动选最佳方法，--withtool 用指定包管理器，--sys 用系统包管理器。\n想先看看会执行什么命令？加 --printcmd 预览，确认后再执行。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Automating software install in scripts? Three ways to choose:\n--best auto-selects by priority, --withtool uses a specified package manager, --sys uses the system package manager.\nWant to see what commands will run? Add --printcmd to preview, then execute when ready.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"让 AI Agent 帮用户装软件：--search 从多个来源搜索找到合适的软件，\n--printinfo 获取安装方法和元数据，\n两者结合就能给出针对性的安装建议。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Help users install software via AI Agent: use --search to discover software across sources,\nand --printinfo for install methods and metadata —\nthen make informed recommendations.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"--search 跨多个软件源（apt、brew、pixi、npm 等）和 skill 平台（skills.sh、clawhub.ai 等）聚合搜索。\n加 --package 仅搜软件源，加 --skill 仅搜 skill 平台。\n"
,
"en"
:
"--search aggregates across multiple package sources (apt, brew, pixi, npm, etc.) and skill platforms (skills.sh, clawhub.ai, etc.).\nAdd --package to search only package sources, --skill to search only skill platforms.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"--env 感知当前系统环境（平台、架构、发行版等），\n--available-tool 查询当前系统支持的包管理器，加 --installed 仅显示已安装的。\n"
,
"en"
:
"--env detects the current system environment (platform, architecture, distro, etc.),\nand --available-tool lists supported package managers; add --installed to show installed only.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"支持前缀格式快速指定安装来源：brew/jq、apt/git、npm/express、sys/bun、best/jq。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Prefix format for quick source selection: brew/jq, apt/git, npm/express, sys/bun, best/jq.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"--printcmd 可与 --best、--withtool、--sys 组合使用，预演而不执行。\n"
,
"en"
:
"--printcmd can be combined with --best, --withtool, --sys to preview without executing.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"skill 默认安装到全局环境中。如需更细致的控制，请使用 x skill（文档：https://x-cmd.com/mod/skill）。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Skills are installed in the global environment by default. For more fine-grained control, use x skill (docs: https://x-cmd.com/mod/skill).\n"
}
]
,
"#subcmd:Install"
:
[
"--run"
,
"--best"
,
"--sys"
,
"--withtool"
]
,
"#subcmd:Info"
:
[
"--ls"
,
"--printinfo|--cat"
,
"--printcmd|--dry-run"
,
"--search"
,
"--env"
,
"--available-tool"
]
,
"#subcmd:Interactive"
:
[
"--fzf|--fz"
]
,
"#subcmd:Maintenance"
:
[
"--update|-u"
]
,
"--ls"
:
{
"#subcmd"
:
true
,
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"List all software supported by the install module"
,
"cn"
:
"列出 install 模块收录的所有软件"
}
,
"--tsv"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Output the full software index in TSV format"
,
"cn"
:
"以 TSV 格式输出完整的软件索引"
}
}
,
"--csv"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Output the full software index in CSV format"
,
"cn"
:
"以 CSV 格式输出完整的软件索引"
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x install --ls"
,
"en"
:
"List all supported software (interactive UI in terminal)"
,
"cn"
:
"列出所有支持的软件（终端下启用交互 UI）"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x install --ls --tsv"
,
"en"
:
"Output all software index in TSV format"
,
"cn"
:
"以 TSV 格式输出所有软件索引"
}
]
}
,
"--fzf|--fz"
:
{
"#subcmd"
:
true
,
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Enable the interactive fzf UI for the install module"
,
"cn"
:
"启用 install 模块的 fzf 交互式 UI"
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x install"
,
"en"
:
"Enable the interactive fzf UI for the install module"
,
"cn"
:
"启用 install 模块的 fzf 交互式 UI"
}
]
}
,
"--printinfo|--cat"
:
{
"#subcmd"
:
true
,
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Print detailed information and all installation methods for a software (without executing)"
,
"cn"
:
"打印软件的详细信息和所有安装方法（不执行）"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Software name to query"
,
"cn"
:
"要查询的软件名"
}
,
"#exec:stdout"
:
"xrc install; ___x_cmd_install_ls___name"
}
,
"--json"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Output in JSON format (for AI Agent)"
,
"cn"
:
"以 JSON 格式输出（供 AI Agent 使用）"
}
}
,
"--yml"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Output in YAML format"
,
"cn"
:
"以 YAML 格式输出"
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x install --printinfo bun"
,
"en"
:
"Print detailed information and all installation methods for a bun"
,
"cn"
:
"打印 bun 的详细信息和所有安装方法"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x install --printinfo --json bun"
,
"en"
:
"Output bun detailed info and all methods in JSON format"
,
"cn"
:
"以 JSON 格式输出 bun 的详细信息和所有安装方法"
}
]
}
,
