:
"Print only tool names"
}
}
,
"--tsv"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"以 TSV 格式输出"
,
"en"
:
"Output in TSV format"
}
}
,
"--csv"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"以 CSV 格式输出"
,
"en"
:
"Output in CSV format"
}
}
,
"--app"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"使用交互式 app 查看"
,
"en"
:
"View in interactive app mode"
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x install --available-tool"
,
"en"
:
"List all supported package managers (including not-yet-installed)"
,
"cn"
:
"列出所有支持的包管理器（含未安装的）"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x install --available-tool --installed"
,
"en"
:
"List only installed package managers"
,
"cn"
:
"仅列出已安装的包管理器"
}
]
}
,
"--run"
:
{
"#subcmd"
:
true
,
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Run the installation command to install software (interactive selection by default)"
,
"cn"
:
"运行安装命令安装软件（默认交互式选择）"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Software name, or prefixed format like brew/jq, sys/git, best/bun"
,
"cn"
:
"软件名，或带前缀格式如 brew/jq、sys/git、best/bun"
}
,
"#exec:stdout"
:
"xrc install; ___x_cmd_install_ls___name"
}
,
"--auto"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Automatically route by prefix (brew/*, apt/*, npm/*, sys/*, best/*, etc.)"
,
"cn"
:
"根据前缀自动路由（brew/*、apt/*、npm/*、sys/*、best/* 等）"
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x install git"
,
"en"
:
"Interactively select and run a Git installation command"
,
"cn"
:
"交互式选择并运行 Git 的安装命令"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x install --auto brew/jq"
,
"en"
:
"Automatically install jq using brew"
,
"cn"
:
"自动使用 brew 安装 jq"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x install --auto best/bun"
,
"en"
:
"Automatically select the best method to install bun"
,
"cn"
:
"自动选择最佳方式安装 bun"
}
]
}
,
"--best"
:
{
"#subcmd"
:
true
,
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Automatically select the best installation method based on priority"
,
"cn"
:
"根据优先级自动选择最佳安装方法"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Software name(s) to install"
,
"cn"
:
"要安装的软件名"
}
,
"#exec:stdout"
:
"xrc install; ___x_cmd_install_ls___name"
}
,
"-p|--priority"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Comma-separated tool priority list (e.g. brew,apt,uv)"
,
"cn"
:
"逗号分隔的工具优先级列表（如 brew,apt,uv）"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Priority list"
,
"cn"
:
"工具优先级列表"
}
}
}
,
"--printcmd|--dry-run"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"打印最佳安装命令但不执行"
,
"en"
:
"Print the best install command without executing"
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x install --best bun"
,
"en"
:
"Automatically select the best method to install bun"
,
"cn"
:
"自动选择最佳方式安装 bun"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x install --best --printcmd bun"
,
"en"
:
"Print the best install command for bun without executing"
,
"cn"
:
"打印安装 bun 的最佳命令但不执行"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x install --best --priority brew,xpkg bun"
,
"en"
:
"Install bun with brew as priority, falling back to xpkg"
,
"cn"
:
"优先使用 brew 安装 bun，其次 xpkg"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x install --best bun vim"
,
"en"
:
"Batch install using best method"
,
"cn"
:
"使用最佳方式批量安装"
}
]
}
,
"--sys"
:
{
"#subcmd"
:
true
,
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Install using the system package manager (brew, apt, dnf, apk, etc.)"
,
"cn"
:
"使用系统包管理器安装（brew、apt、dnf、apk 等）"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Software name to install"
,
"cn"
:
"要安装的软件名"
}
,
"#exec:stdout"
:
"xrc install; ___x_cmd_install_ls___name"
}
,
"--direct"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Skip recorded methods and directly use the system package manager to install"
,
"cn"
:
"不查找收录的安装方法，直接使用系统包管理器尝试安装"
}
}
,
"--printcmd|--dry-run"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"打印系统包管理器的安装命令但不执行"
,
"en"
:
"Print the system package manager install command without executing"
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x install --sys bun"
,
"en"
:
"Install bun using the system package manager"
,
"cn"
:
"使用系统包管理器安装 bun"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x install --sys --printcmd bun"
,
"en"
:
"Print the system package manager install command for bun"
,
"cn"
:
"打印系统包管理器安装 bun 的命令"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x install --sys --direct bun"
,
"en"
:
"Directly use system package manager to install bun (skip recorded methods)"
,
"cn"
:
"直接使用系统包管理器安装 bun（不查找收录的安装方法）"
}
]
}
,
"--withtool"
:
{
"#subcmd"
:
true
,
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Install using a specified package manager"
,
"cn"
:
"使用指定的包管理器安装"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Package manager name (brew, apt, npm, pip, go, cargo, pixi, pkgx, etc.)"
,
"cn"
:
"包管理器名称（brew、apt、npm、pip、go、cargo、pixi、pkgx 等）"
}
}
,
"#2"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Software name(s) to install"
,
"cn"
:
"要安装的软件名"
}
,
"#exec:stdout"
:
"xrc install; ___x_cmd_install_ls___name"
}
,
"--direct"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Skip recorded methods and directly use the package manager to install"
,
"cn"
:
"不查找收录的安装方法，直接使用指定包管理器尝试安装"
}
}
,
"--printcmd"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"打印指定包管理器的安装命令但不执行"
,
"en"
:
"Print the install command for the specified tool without executing"
}
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"默认查找收录的安装方法。加 --direct 不查找收录的安装方法，直接调用包管理器：\nx install --withtool brew bun — 查找 brew 安装 bun 的收录方法\nx install --withtool brew --direct bun — 直接用 brew 安装 bun\n"
,
"en"
:
"By default, looks up recorded installation methods. Use --direct to skip and call the package manager directly:\nx install --withtool brew bun — look up recorded brew method for bun\nx install --withtool brew --direct bun — directly install bun via brew\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x install --withtool brew vim bun"
,
"en"
:
"Install vim and bun using brew"
,
"cn"
:
"使用 brew 安装 vim 和 bun"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x install --withtool brew --printcmd vim bun"
,
"en"
:
"Print brew install commands for vim and bun without executing"
,
"cn"
:
"打印 brew 安装 vim 和 bun 的命令但不执行"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x install --withtool brew --direct bun"
,
"en"
:
"Directly install bun via brew (skip recorded methods)"
,
"cn"
:
"直接用 brew 安装 bun（不查找收录的安装方法）"
}
]
}
,
"--search"
:
{
"#subcmd"
:
true
,
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Search for software and skills across multiple package sources and skill platforms"
,
"cn"
:
"从多个软件源和 skill 平台聚合搜索软件和 skill"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Search keyword"
,
"cn"
:
"搜索关键词"
}
}
,
"--package"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Search only in package sources (apt, brew, pixi, npm, etc.)"
,
"cn"
:
"仅从软件源中搜索（apt、brew、pixi、npm 等）"
}
}
,
"--skill"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Search only in skill platforms (skills.sh, clawhub.ai, etc.)"
,
"cn"
:
"仅从 skill 平台中搜索（skills.sh、clawhub.ai 等）"
}
}
,
"--json"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Output in JSON format (for AI Agent)"
,
"cn"
:
"以 JSON 格式输出（供 AI Agent 使用）"
}
}
,
"--tsv"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Output in TSV format"
,
"cn"
:
"以 TSV 格式输出"
}
}
,
"--csv"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Output in CSV format"
,
"cn"
:
"以 CSV 格式输出"
}
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x install --search ppt"
,
"en"
:
"Search for software and skills matching \"ppt\" across all sources"
,
"cn"
:
"从所有来源搜索匹配 \"ppt\" 的软件和 skill"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x install --search --package pdf"
,
"en"
:
"Search for PDF-related software in package sources only"
,
